commit message: Fix lyrics refreshing when they shouldn't
Implement reading Lyrics and Artwork from id3 tags (close #43)
Fix exception with .equals() when URL was null
Show toast message when importing an invalid musicID message (close #37)
Fix wrong color in menus for some users
Add subtitle when the lyrics come from the id3 metadata, make it possible to force a download, disable automatic refresh when lyrics come from id3 metadata
Fix BadParcelableException causing the app to crash (w/ Winamp Shoutcast for instance)
Use LyricsWiki Json API instead of Jsoup

Merge pull request #70 from beschoenen/master

Implement search for JLyric
Fix artwork not being rescaled properly
Fix double notifications on some devices
Make it easy to search when lyrics can't be found (close #32)
Fix potential memory leak in LyricsTextFactory when creating Typefaces
Ignore case when sorting saved lyrics
Remove hiragana mention in the J-Lyric option label (close #69)
Fix issues when metadata contains + sign
Use Material Design for dialogs and switches on 4.x
Show animation when leaving search activity
Fix long delay when importing from musicID where the screen was empty
Fix some results being unavailable on LyricWiki
Protect server against massive hits from client by moving Bollywood at the end of the list
Fix issue where auto refresh would happen after clicking search results
Change search suggestions to grey in amber theme
Fix broken build for play variant
Fix crash for users from older versions who had enabled certain providers
Fix NullPointerException happning before menu has been created
